Q. Calculate the week, days and month left in your life 
INPUT:

age = int(input("What is your current age : "))#if your end age is 90

day = 365*90 - age*365
week = 52*90 - age*52
month = 12*90 - age*12

print(f"You have {day} days,{week} weeks and {month} months left ")

#                              or
age = int(input("What is your current age : "))#if your end age is 90

remaining_age = 90 - age
day = remaining_age * 365
week = remaining_age * 52
month = remaining_age * 12

print(f"You have {day} days,{week} weeks and {month} months left ")

OUTPUT:
    
You have 26280 days,3744 weeks and 864 months left 

